      {
        "title": "Great case with the option for touchscreen later",
        "text": "Well built and easy to set up. It came well packed and nothing missing. However there are a few issues. If you have any other full length pcie cards they may not fit as the case is set up for half height cards other than the vertical graphics card. Documentation wise it isn't the clearest but there are many many videos on the company site and generally on the internet that answer all the questions I had. It is lacking on storage bays there is plenty of room for more 2,5 and 3,5 bays that could have been added.\nDespite the few issues I am really pleased with this case overall. It looks good, does its job very well and is great for cooling and cable management.",
